{
  "texts": [
    "Aithal and Aithal (2023) argue that ChatGPT plays a substantial role in guiding students through exploratory inquiries -an essential part of the development of their academic and research skills.",
    "Moreover, ChatGPT assists postgraduate students in constructing error-free sentences that are accepted in academic writing (Sallam, 2023).",
    "In addition to academic assistance, ChatGPT plays a pivotal role in enhancing postgraduate students' confidence and interest in research by providing guidance on how to conduct scientific research.",
    "Fatimah (2018) asserts that academic writing is a crucial skill that students must possess to generate highquality work.",
    "Thus, ChatGPT serves as a comprehensive support system throughout the research journey, assisting postgraduate students with both academic and personal aspects (Tiunova & Muñoz, 2023)."
  ]
}